      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts as it should, making it a reliable choice for any commute. While the exterior and interior are clean and presentable, you may find some minor cosmetic wear and small scratches consistent with regular use. Overall, this is a solid, dependable car that offers a great balance of quality and value without the premium price of a mint-condition showpiece.",
