    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver. While the engine and transmission are solid, the car shows its age with some interior wear and minor suspension noise. It\u2019s an ideal choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a reasonable price, though it may require some minor maintenance down the line.",
